### Configuration
@api_key = supersecretapikey
@base_url = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check (no API key needed)
GET {{base_url}}/health

### Get all books with full details
GET {{base_url}}/api/books/
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get specific book by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/books/1
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Create new book with copies
POST {{base_url}}/api/books/
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Hobbit",
  "isbn": "9780547928227",
  "year_published": 1937,
  "copies_count": 2
}

### Borrow a copy (copy_id=2, user_id=1 in header)
POST {{base_url}}/api/books/copies/2/borrow
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
X-User-Id: 1

### Return a copy (copy_id=1)
POST {{base_url}}/api/books/copies/1/return
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

