### USERS ENDPOINTS
###

### Get all users
GET {{base_url}}/api/users/
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get specific user by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/users/1
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Create new user
POST {{base_url}}/api/users/
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
